  "texts": [
    "The milestone where AI, supposing, reaches human intelligence was called by Vernor Vinge, the \"singularity.\"",
    "This notion has been popularized by the futurist scholar and director of Google Engineering, Ray Kurzweil.",
    "There is in my opinion a serious methodological problem concerning the possible proof that a machine has surpassed the human level of intelligence.",
    "This would require a proof that for every conceivable human goal, the machine achieves better performance.",
    "So far, this has been accomplished for particular goals by the direct competition of a human expert and a machine."
  ],
